The Foreign Affairs Network (FAN)

The Foreign Affairs Network (FAN), developed under the Department of State's Bureau of Information Resource Management (IRM), is a portfolio of secure, cloud-based services that enable a more mobile, productive, and collaborative workforce. Users can request an account by accessing, completing, and submitting the DS-7771 Form on myData. Please follow the instructions on the form and complete all required fields.

To learn more please reach out to support@fan.gov
